Package: ridgregextra
Type: Package
Title: Ridge Regression Parameter Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Filiz Karadag, Hakan Savas Sazak, Olgun Aydin
Maintainer: Olgun Aydin <olgun.aydin@pg.edu.pl>
Description: It is a package that provides alternative approach for finding optimum parameters of ridge regression. This package includes a procedure finding the ridge parameter value k which makes the VIF values closest to 1 while keeping them above 1 as in Kutner et al. (2004). It presents a system that automatically determines the k value in a certain range and gives the ridge regression results. Finally it shows three sets of graphs consisting k versus VIF values, regression coefficents and standard errors of them.
